body:
### About Me
When I'm not coding, I like to roast coffee, brew beer, and play board games! One day I'll have a website dedicated to all of these, but I'm currently working on Boardy - a tabletop game picker app. 

### Contact
I'd love to help you out on your next big project!  

You can email me at josh@joshstricklin.com
or reach me on Twitter - [@josh_stricklin](https://twitter.com/josh_stricklin).
